{"tid":2059704,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】孫藝珍着小背心曬健康美　2年前舊廣告花絮相仲吸睛","createTime":"2020-06-11T06:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T07:41:00.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2893a63cc9e3dbf180e1e49df50a6b2ba4a3a3d","tid":2059704,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T06:02:51.000Z","msg":"孫藝珍與玄彬合拍《愛的迫降》後人氣急升，今年38歲的她近日更成為「2020全球最美女星」第一位，撃敗女團BLACKPINK Lisa和TWICE子瑜！又一次爆紅的孫藝珍當然不放過搵錢機會，近日公司就公開了她拍攝廣告的花絮片，女神穿上小背心大曬性感健康美。<br />\n<br />\n所屬公司日前公開孫藝珍為美妝品牌ma:nyo拍攝廣告的花絮片，不足45秒的影片中，孫藝珍換足三套衫，完美消化各種風格。當中最吸睛可說是深色背心配白色緊身牌的造型，小背心凸顯她的好身材，散發出一陣性感健康美。翻找過去孫藝珍與不同品牌雜誌合作的拍攝花絮，當中亦有不少照片相當吸睛，讀者不妨回顧一下。"},{"pid":"bda8998ec1f7611a73bc5fd07e0feb04e3e7a267","tid":2059704,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200611/347733811276156928.jpeg/69__30M7HxX7wjg-iPyQkHbdibcMzWp9sge-YbIHvmE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200611%2F347733811276156928.jpeg%2F69__30M7HxX7wjg-iPyQkHbdibcMzWp9sge-YbIHvmE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c3aba599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200611/347734239208411136.jpeg/c_2yGaVkflhYskoBK3VsyRC5bTnhU6dCOdTYijnU2Io?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200611%2F347734239208411136.jpeg%2Fc_2yGaVkflhYskoBK3VsyRC5bTnhU6dCOdTYijnU2Io%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=421739db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200611/347734243503378432.jpeg/CeapjkpWCO5LiNAAnKk9GSGqGLeA0qLvN1pQRjdaUEY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200611%2F347734243503378432.jpeg%2FCeapjkpWCO5LiNAAnKk9GSGqGLeA0qLvN1pQRjdaUEY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b1f9e054&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"459ab07e5e391bcafd5c9f6cb619b573db85c6df","tid":20597